original_title: Matthew Hardy Live - I'm So Australian
overview: Recorded live at the National Theatre, it is an hour of comedy power. Not only does Matthew deliver close-to 100 "I'm So Australian" lines which are set to become a part of our everyday speech & the hottest catch-cry this summer, he tackles a number of other topics too.
tagline: Matthew Hardy's dynamic show speaks of the year Australia became obsessed with itself.
title: Matthew Hardy Live - I'm So Australian
